premise_source_doc_sentence: Reginald James `` Reg '' Watson AM  (  born 1926  )  , is an Australian retired television producer , best known for creating soap operas like Prisoner and Neighbours .
Until Tomorrow  (  1975  )  was an Australian television soap opera created by Reg Watson .

It was created by TV executive Reg Watson , who proposed the idea of making a show that focused on realistic stories and portrayed adults and teenagers who talk openly and solve their problems together .

At Changing Our World , Watson created onPhilanthropy , an online resource for philanthropy professionals ; he often comments on and writes frequently about the intersection of media and philanthropy .
As a member of the Expert and Technical Committee of the Royal Automobile Club , Watson created specially designed instruments to investigate and develop the petrol motor .
Until Tomorrow was Reg Watson 's first Australian soap opera .
